Description: 
    Utility functions to download and process data produced by the ALARM Project, 
    including 2020 redistricting files <https://alarm-redist.org/posts/2021-08-10-census-2020/> 
    and 50-State Redistricting Simulations <doi:10.7910/DVN/SLCD3E>. The package
    extends functionality introduced in <arXiv:2206.10763> to cover states with
    only a single district.
